==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sledding
<hw>Sled"ding</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of transporting or riding on a sled.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of the snow which admits of the running of
sleds; <as>as, the <ex>sledding</ex> is good</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sledge</ent>⟦br⟧
